The paper discusses an algorithm for separating points in n-dimensional space, which is a common problem in computational geometry (cs.CG) and data structures (cs.DS). The algorithm also involves making optimal use of information, which is a key aspect of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the application of the algorithm to data retrieval problems in medical databases, which falls under the category of databases (cs.DB).
